title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 3 Night' game
title_page: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 3 Night' game
maintext:
BOISE, Idaho (AP) _ The winning numbers in Friday evening’s drawing of the Idaho Lottery’s “Pick 3 Night” game were:
1-8-9
(one, eight, nine)
